{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"43229-chunu-munu-it-s-freezing","title":"Chunu & Munu: It's Freezing!","description":"Chunu and Munu wake up on a freezing cold morning. They can’t find their warm clothes! Where can the clothes be?","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Alisha Berger"],"illustrators":["Abin  Shrestha"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/43229-chunu-munu-it-s-freezing"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101410/size3/9d1ab657164a00bed5d792be5509c5c0.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101410/size6/9d1ab657164a00bed5d792be5509c5c0.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79307/size6/954746f5f608776ab233aeaafc0f64ef.jpg","text":"Look! \nThe sun is rising.\nThe birds are chirping.\nThe girls are ready to play.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79308/size6/030ac172987514ce004fc6793d40ffde.jpg","text":"Chunu says, “Brrr, how cold!”\nMunu says, “Yes, so cold!”","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79309/size6/75a1145a8d55137972e1cdc3e8af25fb.jpg","text":"Chunu says, “I will wear warm clothes to protect myself from the cold.”","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79310/size6/ee56094d9793e54c6c5d71ba72f98351.jpg","text":"“Where's my warm hat?\" Chunu wonders.\n\"It was here yesterday.\nWhere has it gone today?”","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79311/size6/b5a51d8e74f50a6ea216840034baa668.jpg","text":"“I can't find my warm socks!\" Munu cries.\n\"Where are my  warm socks?”","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79312/size6/5ed5e11abd302c886a7a0efecc7f06cc.jpg","text":"“My feet are so cold, they're numb!”\n“Mine too,” Munu tells her sister.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79313/size6/9c543d72c44e34ae604dbca4af7d71ed.jpg","text":"“Brrr, so cold!”\n“It's so cold!”\nThe girls shiver.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79314/size6/90a52df4fd497ad0de715c7f5050da98.jpg","text":"“We can't find my warm hat.\nWe can't find your warm socks.\nWe can't find anything,” Chunu says.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79315/size6/e318dd546e5de91afbf001a5597287aa.jpg","text":"“Where could our clothes possibly be?\"Munu wonders.\n“Here is my warm coat!\" Chunu says. \n\"But where are my other clothes?”","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79316/size6/017a871558f9a73ed57b3bc8f365ae6b.jpg","text":"“Chunu, look here,\" Munu cries.\n\"Look into the hole.\nThere are my warm socks.\nThere is your warm hat.”","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79317/size6/3488098cc069a2baaea78d1e9dbab230.jpg","text":"Chunu and Munu looked inside the hole.\nThey took their socks and warm hat and went to find all their other warm things.\nThen they would play!","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79318/size6/09fc3d6be83bfbf1a7001807236da491.jpg","text":"13/13","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":12,"words":173}}